    <p>This website explores various aspects of data privacy including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Importance of data privacy for individuals and organizations</li>
      <li>Challenges in maintaining privacy</li>
      <li>New Zealand's Privacy Act 2020 and its principles</li>
      <li>GDPR and its global impact</li>
    </ul>
  </main>

